    "desc": "Low rates, convenient locations. Nusenda is the largest federal credit union in New Mexico. Employees serve and give back to the community. Routing #307083665",
    "navbar": "LOCATIONS CAREERS ABOUT CONTACT",
    "text": "LOCATIONS CAREERS ABOUT CONTACT\nAsk\nRouting Number (ABA): 307083665\nAccounts\nLoans & Credit Cards\nMortgages\nInvestments\nBusiness\nMember Benefits\nNews & Resources\n●●●●●\nLog In To Your Account\nJoin or Apply Today!\nBecome a Member\nApply for a Mortgage\nApply for a Loan\nMake an Appointment\n\nThe Power of WE®\nWe're Nusenda Credit Union — around for nearly a century, but continually reinventing what we do and how we do it, to better serve your financial needs.\n\nInstead of being nickeled and dimed with unnecessary fees — we put money back in your pocket. We’re a credit union — with all of the services a big bank has to offer — plus added benefits simply for being a member. And because we’re a not-for-profit, we pay back earnings to you with higher savings rates and lower loan rates, using the best tools to keep your money safe.\n\nThink about us as your banking partner — trusted advisor — champion.\nMember Benefits\nEarn Your Return\n\n\nCommunity Rewards\n\n\nLocations\n\n\n\nTechnology\n\n\nMember Savings\n\n\nPower of WE\n\n\nEducation\n\n\nRates\nAuto Credit Card Home Equity Deposits\nAuto\nSince we’re a credit union, we offer competitive rates on everything from auto loans and credit cards to home equity loans and certificates. Click on the buttons below for more product information, comparisons with other institutions and more. Note that Nusenda rates used are the best rates currently available.\nSee All Auto Loan Rates*\nNews & Resources\n \nNewsroom\n\nSecurity Alerts\n\nFinancial Library\n\nCalculators\n\nSite Map\nPolicies and Disclosures\n\nRouting Number: 307083665\nNMLS: 477659\nFederally insured by NCUA. Your savings are insured to at least $250,000 and backed by the full faith and credit of the United States Government, National Credit Union Administration, a U.S. Government Agency.\n\nEqual Opportunity Lender. We do business in accordance with the Federal Fair Housing Law and the Equal Credit Opportunity Act.\n©2022 Nusenda Credit Union. All Rights Reserved.",
